QuestData.Title: A Worthy Challenge: Wing Leader Ner'onok
QuestData.Description: $n, I need you to assemble an eagle-eyed group and lead them into the Siege of Niuzao Temple. Activate the Challenger's Orb and ground Wing Leader Ner'onok.$B$BReturn to me when you've completed this challenge, and I shall reward you handsomely.
